value.0: Yo... What brings you to my lovely home here in the most luxurious place on Viscara?
Yeah! Beautiful place... Cheap rent... Great neighbours... No complaints from me! Say... Since you're here, wanna give me a hand?
Well, I saw this cool design in a magazine for some cool new rags... I only need a few things... <StartAction>[He holds out a list]</Start>
Hey hey! Do you have those things for me?
Thanks for that! Say, you've been a real help... Think you can help me again?
I heard this guy playing an electric guitar, and I want to try make one myself... I just need a few things. <StartAction>[He holds out another list.]</Start>
Hey! Any chance finding those electrical things?
Oh nice! Will give that a try later... Say, think you can help again?
Well, you see... My ma's in a home and her rocking chair just broke. So, I was gonna make her a new one... <StartAction>[Another list is held out.]</Start>
Nice, you're back! Got the wood yet?
Amazing! Now my Ma is gonna have the best chair in the home... Wanna go again?

I heard some of my neighbour's talking about how the air on Viscara is poisonous, and they gave me this protein shake recipe to stop it from damaging my lungs... <StartAction>[He holds out the list.]</Start>
You're back! Quick, did you find the meat for this shake?
Nice! Now I just need to find a blender to mix all of this up... Say, you wanna help me with my picnic blanket problem now?
Oh... This will be -easy-. I need some rocks to hold the corners down so I can enjoy my picnics... <StartAction>[He holds out the list... again.]</Start>
Rock on! How'd you get on finding those rocks?
Solid! These will make sure it doesn't move at all... Now... Hmm.. I wonder...
Oh... Well... I'm running low on my herbs, and they help with my jam sessions... Think you could, you know, help a guy out? <StartAction>[He slowly extends another list.]</Start>
You managed to get my herbs yet?
Right on! Now I can carry on with my jam... Hmm... Hmmmmmm... Hmmmmmmmm....

I was just looking around, and... Every home deserves decorations, right? So... I was thinking about adding some wow to mine... Reckon you could... <StartAction>[That slow reach out with a list in his hands.]</Start>
Ooohhh! You have my decorations for me?
Now this place is going to look amazing! Helga's house will have nothing on mine now... Now... All I need is one more thing...

There was these two guys in hoods a couple weeks ago, and they were talking about these shiny shards that can be found on some bigger creatures on Dathomir. I have no idea, but I think it'd look pretty cool hung up in the center of the room.
Did you manage to figure out what I was thinking of?

That's it! Thank you... you've done all of this for me, so... Take these! I found them in a sewer pipe a couple months ago, and I have no idea what they are, but maybe you will. <StartAction>[He holds out a bundled up schematic.]</Start>
Hey, thanks again for all your help! If I ever need help again, i'll be sure to reach out! Think you can get me a datapad so I can call you whenever I need?
I got lost, and ended up here somehow. Do you actually live down here?
Not really... Have a good day.
I guess... What do you need?
Ah, sorry... I'm a little busy. Another time?
Oh, yeah sure. I can help. <StartAction>[You take the list.]</Start>
Not yet, no.
I think I've got everything on the list...
Maybe another time.
I guess... What do you need this time?
On second thought, I don't have the time...
<StartAction>[You take the list.]</Start> Sure, I can do that, I guess.
Not quite.
I think so? Here.
Another time...
What's the deal this time?
I haven't got time to chop trees, sorry.
How could I say no to that? <StartAction>[You take the list.]</Start>
Not exactly... I'll be back.
This wasn't too bad... Here you go.
I've already done you three favours... So, no...
Again... What do you need this time?
That sounds like a load of rubbish. You're on your own.
I don't believe that for a second, but I'd rather not risk your health... <StartAction>[You take the list... Again.]</Start>
Getting meat isn't as easy as you'd think.
Yeah... Took a bit, but I got all the meat.
I'm not even going to ask... I'm just gonna go.
...I have a feeling you're going to ask me to get you some more things...
I'm sure you can find some rocks in here to use... Good luck... Be seeing you.
Rocks... I... Sure... <StartAction>[You take the list... Once more.]</Start>
Rocks are harder to find then I thought... I'll be back.
Did you just say-... You know what, nevermind... Here.
Before you even ask, no... I'm going.
... What now? What on Viscara could you possibly need now?
Nope. I'm done. You can find your own herbs.
... Sure... I've done this much already, whats one more? <StartAction>[And you take the list... Again.]</Start>
Not quite, I wanted to ask what these are actually for... But, nevermind. Be back soon.
Yes, I do. Here you go...
I'm leaving... Good luck with whatever this is.
Just spit it out already...
You live in a sewer... It's not going to get any better... Bye.
<StartAction>[You just take the list and walk away saying nothing else.]</Start>
No. You'll get them when I feel ready!
Yeah... This one was a bit of a pain, but I managed to get them all.
You're on your own. Bye.
... And what is this one thing...
Yeah, you can go get that yourself.
I know what they are... Let me see what I can do.
You have no idea how hard they are to get, and how expensive they are...
Yes... Here.
<StartAction>[You take the schematic.]</Start> Atleast... This was all worth it...
<StartAction>[You just turn and walk away before he can ask anything else.]</Start>
